{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"date: 2016-06-02T23:40:30-05:00"}],"primaryContentSections":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If everyone is shouting then joining them only adds to the noise. The first person to shout gets a reward but each person after her gets less. It doesn’t add to impact or success but instead makes the world a little bit worse. It drives away anyone who is following closely — those who truly care about what you’re doing."}]}],"kind":"content"}],"kind":"article","topicSectionsStyle":"detailedGrid","identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/Brunow\/documentation\/Brunow\/06-02-everyone-is-shouting","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"sections":[],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/brunow\/06-02-everyone-is-shouting"]}],"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/Brunow\/documentation\/Brunow","doc:\/\/Brunow\/documentation\/Brunow\/Archive","doc:\/\/Brunow\/documentation\/Brunow\/2016"]]},"metadata":{"title":"Everyone Is Shouting","platforms":[{"introducedAt":"2017.01.20","name":"Brunow"}],"modules":[{"name":"Brunow"}],"color":{"standardColorIdentifier":"purple"}},"references":{"doc://Brunow/documentation/Brunow/Archive":{"role":"collectionGroup","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"All posts"}],"title":"Archive","identifier":"doc:\/\/Brunow\/documentation\/Brunow\/Archive","type":"topic","kind":"article","url":"\/documentation\/brunow\/archive"},"doc://Brunow/documentation/Brunow/2016":{"url":"\/documentation\/brunow\/2016","type":"topic","title":"2016","kind":"article","role":"collectionGroup","identifier":"doc:\/\/Brunow\/documentation\/Brunow\/2016","abstract":[]},"doc://Brunow/documentation/Brunow":{"url":"\/documentation\/brunow","role":"collection","identifier":"doc:\/\/Brunow\/documentation\/Brunow","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"David Brunow, known as Brunow [ˈbɹunoʊ] to the folks he works with, is a human living on Earth. You mi